  "text": "Stability of the 2Fe-2S Cluster. It was previously shown that the 2Fe-2S cluster of native mitoNEET is labile and that the rate (defined as the reciprocal of the half-life of visible absorption) of cluster loss is first-order with respect to proton concentration [CITATION_1] . Since the 2Fe-2S metal center of mitoNEET has strong visible absorption bands, the cluster loss was monitored by the disappearance of the visible absorbance peak near 460 nm. Decay curves and fits are presented as Supporting Information.",
